# [[project_name]]

Flutter project generated with **Flutterator** (DDD / clean architecture).

## Stack

- `flutter_bloc`, `freezed`, `injectable`, `get_it`, `go_router`, `dio`, `retrofit`, `dartz`, `caravaggio_ui` **1.0.6**

## Where code goes

| Need | Location |
|------|----------|
| Shared domain entity | `lib/domain/<entity>/model/` + `infrastructure/` |
| Enum | `lib/domain/enums/` |
| Feature with BLoC | `lib/features/<feature>/application/` + `presentation/` |
| Reusable UI component | `lib/features/components/<name>/` |
| App-wide widgets | `lib/widgets/common/` |

## How to build features

Use skill **`/epic-delivery`** with a high-level description. Epics are tracked in `docs/epics/`.

For presentation UI use skill **`/caravaggio-ui`** and read `docs/architecture/CARAVAGGIO_COMPONENTS.md`.

Agents write Dart **directly** — do not run `flutterator` CLI.

